[normal]The other thing I probably should have said in my opening statement is that when we talk about youth unemployment and concerns about employability of young people, it is very easy to tar the whole age group. That is certainly not what we hear from employers. 
[normal]Employers 
[normal]are concerned about the situation at the moment because they 
