[normal]Richard Exell[bold]: 
[normal]I
[normal]t is not all bleak, Chair. We may have seen a decline in Saturday jobs, but if you think about young people’s employment experience, the biggest change over the last 20 years is the way it has become the norm for people in post-compulsory education to combine that with paid work, even with full-time paid work in some cases. 
